<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Récépissé de livraison — Poulets BF</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bf-green: #2E7D32;
      --bf-green-dark: #14532D;
      --bf-amber: #FF8F00;
      --bf-success: #2E7D32;
      --ink: #0F172A;
      --ink-soft: #475569;
      --ink-muted: #94A3B8;
      --paper: #FFFFFF;
      --border-fine: #D1D5DB;
    }
    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm; margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--paper);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink); font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 12mm 15mm;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding-bottom: 5mm;
      border-bottom: 2pt solid var(--bf-green);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .brand strong { font-size: 18pt; color: var(--bf-green); font-weight: 700; }
    .brand span { display: block; font-size: 8pt; color: var(--ink-muted); }

    .status-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bf-success), #4CAF50);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 2mm 5mm;
      border-radius: 20pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2mm;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1mm;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .order-ref {
      font-size: 12pt;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .order-ref strong { color: var(--bf-amber); }

    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 6mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .info-card {
      padding: 5mm;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border-radius: 3pt;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .info-card h3 {
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
    }
    .info-card dl { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2mm; }
    .info-card dt {
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }
    .info-card dd {
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .delivered-items {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .delivered-items th {
      background: var(--bf-green);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 3mm;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 9pt;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .delivered-items td {
      padding: 3mm;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .delivered-items .right { text-align: right; }
    .delivered-items .check {
      color: var(--bf-success);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .acceptance {
      margin-bottom: 10mm;
      padding: 5mm;
      background: #E8F5E9;
      border-left: 4pt solid var(--bf-success);
      border-radius: 3pt;
    }
    .acceptance h4 {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }
    .acceptance p {
      font-size: 10pt;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
    }

    .signatures {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8mm;
      margin-top: 15mm;
    }
    .sig-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 18mm;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--ink);
    }
    .sig-block strong { display: block; font-size: 10pt; }
    .sig-block span { display: block; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-soft); }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8mm; left: 15mm; right: 15mm;
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      padding-top: 3mm;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="brand">
        <strong>Poulets BF</strong>
        <span>FASO DIGITALISATION · Burkina Faso</span>
      </div>
      <div class="status-badge">✓ Livré</div>
    </header>

    <h1>Récépissé de livraison</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Confirmation de remise de marchandise</p>
    <p class="order-ref">Commande <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> · Livré le <strong>{{dateLivraison}}</strong></p>

    <div style="height: 8mm;"></div>

    <section class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Livré à</h3>
        <dl>
          <div><dt>Nom</dt><dd>{{clientName}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Adresse</dt><dd>{{address}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Téléphone</dt><dd>{{clientPhone}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Réception</dt><dd>{{dateReception}}</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Livreur</h3>
        <dl>
          <div><dt>Nom</dt><dd>{{livreur}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Téléphone</dt><dd>{{livreurPhone}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Origine</dt><dd>{{eleveurName}} · {{eleveurRegion}}</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Trajet</dt><dd>{{distanceKm}} km</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </section>

    <table class="delivered-items">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Article</th>
          <th class="right">Quantité commandée</th>
          <th class="right">Quantité livrée</th>
          <th class="right">État</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <strong>{{race}}</strong><br>
            <span style="color: var(--ink-muted); font-size: 9pt;">Lot {{lotId}}</span>
          </td>
          <td class="right">{{quantityOrdered}}</td>
          <td class="right">{{quantityDelivered}}</td>
          <td class="right check">✓ Conforme</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <section class="acceptance">
      <h4>Déclaration d'acceptation</h4>
      <p>
        Le client, <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>, reconnaît avoir reçu la marchandise
        conforme à la commande <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> en date du <strong>{{dateLivraison}}</strong>.
        Aucune réclamation n'a été formulée au moment de la livraison.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="signatures">
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Le Client</strong>
        <span>{{clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Le Livreur</strong>
        <span>{{livreur}}</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      Récépissé généré automatiquement le {{issuedAt}} · Poulets BF<br>
      Vérification QR : {{verificationUrl}}
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
